00:00:06.450 --> 00:00:08.490
Mobile payments
become streamlined

00:00:08.490 --> 00:00:11.270
with the Payment Request API.

00:00:11.270 --> 00:00:14.340
The Web Bluetooth API is
available experimentally

00:00:14.340 --> 00:00:19.440
on some platforms as an origin
trial, and there's plenty more.

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:20.570
I'm Pete LePage.

00:00:20.570 --> 00:00:24.150
Let's dive in and see what's
new for developers in Chrome 53.

